title: NVIDIA Rolls Out New Quadro & GeForce Drivers for OS X El Capitan
text: NVIDIA has just released a new version of their Quadro & GeForce OS X driver in an effort to add OS X 10.11 El Capitan support and beta support for MacBook Pro and iMac computers with NVIDIA cards. As the changelog for this version of the Quadro & GeForce driver for OS X says, the 346.03.02f01 release includes a graphics driver update to provide OS X El Capitan 10.11 build 15A284 support.
